data.description: WOW, wait no more! Come and tour this beautiful home. Spilt level home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 2 car garage. High Ceilings, Open Floor Plan, complete with a beautiful Fireplace and Huge Living room area. Experience this gorgeous private oasis, completed with an in-ground pool, covered patio, fire pit and 2nd story balcony overlooking the pool. No HOA!
